                        <ContentPresenter HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" x:Name="HeaderContentPresenter" ContentTemplate="{TemplateBinding HeaderTemplate}" Content="{TemplateBinding Header}" FlowDirection="{TemplateBinding FlowDirection}" FontWeight="{ThemeResource ComboBoxHeaderThemeFontWeight}" Margin="0,0,8,0" Visibility="Collapsed" x:DeferLoadStrategy="Lazy"/>
